trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IMultipleViewProvider"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 식별자로 사용 되는 값이 포함 되어 <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IMultipleViewProvider"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: These identifiers are used by UI Automation providers.
trans-unit.target: 이러한 식별자는 UI 자동화 공급자에서 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.MultipleViewPattern>.
